==Funding==

2017: Polkadot raised over 429'000 ETHs in a private and a public sale worth more than $140M at that time. ICO participants are compensated for their contributions as soon as the genesis block is launched and the DOT tokens are created.<ref name="fundraising1">https://techcrunch.com/2017/10/17/polkadot-passes-the-140m-mark-for-its-fund-raise-to-link-private-and-public-blockchains/, accessed on 06.09.2018.</ref><ref name="fundraising2">https://blog.cyber.fund/polkadot-ico-report-b76fbd0b52a2, accessed on 06.09.2018.</ref> However, due to an accident in the code library for the Parity wallet, $98M worth of Ether deposited in a multisig wallet have been frozen and could not be accessed.<ref name="fundraising1"/> Nevertheless, Polkadot stated to continue their work since not all of the funds have been affected by the incident.<ref name="fundraising3">https://medium.com/web3foundation/web-3-multi-sig-wallet-update-245d30df0fb3, accessed on 06.09.2018.</ref> 

